    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "376deb5c-d547-4ca0-b23d-5d7cee2043fc",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "監獄島の亡霊騎士/Ghost of Sgail",
        "Location": "LOCATION_NORTHSEA",
        "PublicId": "121084093341",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/theark/scene_magpie.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 04387b7a-25fa-4dec-baa0-eeff1d36ab11).Image",
        "Description": "この島はかつて監獄島で夜な夜な亡霊となった断罪の騎士が現れるという逸話がある\rなんでもその騎士はこの島に人が集まる日に現れるらしい\r今宵はプロヴィデンスの集会が行われる予定だ\rもしかしたら噂の亡霊騎士も現れるかもしれない\r\rThere is anecdote that this island used to be a prison island and that a knight of absolution who became a ghost appears at night.\rIt is said that the knight appears on days when people gather on the island.\rThere will be a meeting in Providence tonight.\rMaybe the rumored ghost knight will show up.",
        "GameVersion": "8.20.0.76",
        "IsPublished": true,
